imdb.plot outline: Jenn Gotzon shares 20+ years of experience about craftsmanship to marketing secrets, she's learned and developed along the way as an actor, while keeping grounded on an ethical foundation from being raised by a Christian family. Gotzon takes the actor step-by-step through the process of how to create industry buzz like the pros, gaining position above the rest of the crowd, garnering attention that leads to work, and setting them up for success as an industry insider, while staying grounded in humility, servant-hood and unconditional love. Gotzon uses biblical ethics and prayer exercises to inspire actors to find peace and relaxation entering into the mind of the character in a safe way.
